MERDs Bacterial Community Analyses

Lukas Bell-Dereske

9/1/2020

Here is the Code for analyzing the bacterial community composition of MERDS Switchgrass Experiment Lukas (belldere@msu.edu) processed the sequences and subset the larger run to only have samples from MERDS (MERDs 56 of 317 samples in the run)
